 Joe Studwell, author of 'How Asia 
Works: Success and Failure in the World's Most Dynamic Region' 
gives an account of what prompted some economies to take off 
while others lagged. Studwell talks with Bloomberg's Vonnie 
Quinn on  Bloomberg Radio 's "The Hays Advantage."    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:06
 